title: Error in ONNX with max_pool3d
body_html:
hi,
I encountered a problem when I was using ONNX to export a model in which max_pool3d was used, but ceil_mode was False.
The pytorch I am using was downloaded today(27 Dec 2017).
Could anyone help me to solve it?
Thanks a lot!!!!!

UserWarning: ONNX export failed on max_pool3d because torch.onnx.symbolic.max_pool3d does not exist
.format(op_name, op_name))
RuntimeError: ONNX export failed: Couldn't export operator max_pool3d
